  - Anthropic: Claude Sonnet 4, Claude Haiku, Claude 3.5 Sonnet, Claude 3 Haiku
  - Google: Gemini 2.5 Flash, Gemini 2.5 Pro, Gemini 2.0 Flash, Gemini 1.5 Pro
