## Data Flow

### User → Bot
User sends message → Telegram forwards to webhook → Worker stores in D1 → Forwards to admin via Bot API → Admin replies → Worker stores reply → Sends back to user

### User → AI
User selects model → Sends prompt via Mini App → Worker validates API key → Streams response via SSE → Stores conversation in D1

### Widget → Owner
Visitor opens widget → embed.js creates session → Sends message → Worker stores in D1 → Forwards to owner's Telegram → Owner replies → Polled by widget

### Widget → AI
Visitor sends message → Worker checks AI auto-reply → Queries trained context → Generates AI response → Sends back to widget

### Payment
User taps Subscribe → Worker creates Stars invoice → Telegram processes payment → Pre-checkout validation → Successful payment webhook → Worker activates subscription in D1

